    ver2 = list(map(int, ver2.split('.')))
    len_ver1 = len(ver1)
    len_ver2 = len(ver2)
    max_len = max(len_ver1, len_ver2)
    ver1 += [0] * (max_len - len_ver1)
    ver2 += [0] * (max_len - len_ver2)
    if ver1 > ver2:
        return "GT"
    elif ver1 < ver2:
        return "LT"

        return "EQ"
